ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This cog (OPC Server Supporters) is heavily based on the original ServerSupporters 
cog created by AAA3A. The core architecture, event listeners, caching system, 
member scanning logic, and many other fundamental features are derived from 
AAA3A's original work.

Original ServerSupporters cog:
- Author: AAA3A
- Repository: https://github.com/AAA3A-AAA3A/AAA3A-cogs  
- License: MIT License

We have modified the original work to:
- Remove AAA3A_utils dependency
- Add OPC-specific hardcoded values
- Implement announcement-only functionality
- Add live statistics features

Full attribution details can be found in CREDITS.md